 included\nto illustrate the ultimate potential of heating in a realistic scenario in the\nmicrowave regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2016 13:54:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Aug 2016 18:57:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
